	<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<link href="../css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>

	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row content">
			<div class="col-sm-3 sidenav">
				<h4>Awamo Dev Exam App</h4>
				<ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
					<li class="active">
						<a href="#section1">Home</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/api-docs/">API documentation</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<br>
				<div class="input-group">
					<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search">
					<span class="input-group-btn">
						<button class="btn btn-default" type="button">
							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></span>
						</button>
					</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-sm-9">
				<h4><small><b>AWAMO APP</b></small></h4>
					<hr>
						<p>This is an api for awamo practical front-end developer position. The api accepts two numbers and performs basic mathematical calculations of addition,subtraction,division and multiplication. The api gives the result as the expected answer.
							The api expects a json payloadand a post request</p>
				<hr>
				<form role="form">
					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="number1">Number1:</label>
						<input type="text" id="number1" class="form-control">
					</div>

					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="number1">Number2:</label>
						<input type="text" id="number2" class="form-control">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="sel1">elect operation:</label>
						<select class="form-control" id="action">
							<option value="no">Select Operation</option>
							<option value="add">Addition</option>
							<option value="sub">Subtraction</option>
							<option value="div">Division</option>
							<option value="mul">Multiplication</option>
						</select>
					</div>

					<input type="button" class="add-row btn btn-primary" value="perform operation">

				</form>
				<hr>


				<h4>
					<small>
						<b>RESULTS TABLE</b>
					</small>
				</h4>
				<hr>

				<table class="table table-hover">
					<thead>
						<tr style="background:rgb(247, 249, 250)">
							<th>#</th>
							<th>number1</th>
							<th>number2</th>
							<th>response</th>
							<th>expected</th>
							<th>passed</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
					</tbody>
				</table>
				<button type="button" class="delete-row btn btn-danger">Delete Row</button>


				<br>
				<br>



			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

